headline: Cytactic Appoints Veteran Cybersecurity Sales Executive Bill Hogan as Chief Revenue Officer (CRO)
summary: Cytactic, a leader in Cybersecurity Incident Response Management (CIRM), today announced the appointment of Bill Hogan as its new Global Chief Revenue Officer (CRO).
